{"tid":638012,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"海關旺角先達掃場 數十手機店拉閘停業","createTime":"2018-04-22T10:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T14:29:08.000Z","uid":55951,"like":249,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"0a15c75c8e482a64af4b23eb8780619fdddc80cd","tid":638012,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T10:39:02.000Z","msg":"下午4時許，海關突擊搜查專門售賣手機及數碼影音產品的旺角先達廣場，現場消息稱，當時有數十海關人員到場，行動主要針對商場內有店舖疑違法聘用黑工及售賣冒牌手機配件等。受事件影響，有數十間手機店臨時拉閘暫停營業。<br />\n<br />\n據讀者提供的一條片段，當時有多名佩戴委任證的海關人員去到部份手機店調查，現場氣氛緊張，片段中可見有部份手機店在事發時關門拉閘，但仍有其他店舖繼續開門營業，並有市民如常到來選購手機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180421/58102295\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180421%2F58102295&d=lS8Pt5PxRsWfot%2B3CNSdSPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=7b683905\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180421%2F58102295&h=ac00e231\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180421/58102295</a><br />\n<br />\n先達狗今次仲唔仆街<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f25bd924154a343884ab0e1da772c8a56dd7c97d","tid":638012,"uid":26385,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T10:39:21.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703295b48b651427b983060169e2ee679ae4bb61","tid":638012,"uid":40470,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T10:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等佢開返再報控煙辦拉鳩班ST9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76310b8d96f5cf7cb390eb06ba11c7115a8e71e3","tid":638012,"uid":4575,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T10:40:35.000Z","msg":"即係仲開門係正貨店"},{"pid":"1add273a9018ad4a5532840d659997d23d91fa8c","tid":638012,"uid":40470,"like":6,"dislike":47,"score":-41,"quote":{"pid":"76310b8d96f5cf7cb390eb06ba11c7115a8e71e3","tid":638012,"uid":4575,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T10:40:35.000Z","msg":"即係仲開門係正貨店"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T10:43:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n二手機又會比佢攪過<br />\n<br />\n買an機就智力較低既人先會買<br />\n<br />\n買iphone我又諗唔到點解唔去Apple store<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唯一貢獻係呃強國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4b248f6f677d02346aadd438ad8420ed23875b","tid":638012,"uid":55951,"like":70,"dislike":2,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T11:04:06.000Z","msg":"檢獲100部懷疑冒牌或懷疑應用虛假商品說明的智能電話，以及約3,400多件懷疑冒牌智能電話配件，大部份為iPhone，另有小米的電話配件，分別有藍牙耳筒、電池等，估計市值共約150萬元。<br />\n<br />\n海關版權及商標調查科高級監督葉慧嬋表示，偽冒產品仿真度很高，如一些冒牌iPhone或小米的電池，只是行距分隔有差異，以及字體模糊等，一般難以分辨，暫時難以估計有多少經已流入市面。　<br />\n<br />\n他們以將冒牌貨品以原價一成至五成向顧客兜售，甚至將一些舊機翻新、或以<span style=\"color: red;\">水貨作行貨出售</span>，以多種手法魚目混珠，欺騙消費者。<br />\n<br />\n水行貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/22/190350_4505b50a9823e8450a31a63f5ec9848d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F22%2F190350_4505b50a9823e8450a31a63f5ec9848d.png&h=ac54df9e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"edc7db0b32ce78cdc7ac46ff341c6639c95a15f0","tid":638012,"uid":123317,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T11:22:19.000Z","msg":"不如唔爭在執柒左佢重建商場啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1b3d5bd9d04f90c0f76667ef466970a8ed6df0"